  <entry>
    <title>Alpine Linux: unable to select packages</title>
    <link href="/2023/05/08/Alpine-Linux-unable-to-select-packages/"/>
    <url>/2023/05/08/Alpine-Linux-unable-to-select-packages/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>执行<code>apk add npm</code>出现错误：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ERROR: unable to select packages:</span><br><span class="line">  npm (no such package):</span><br><span class="line">    required by: world[npm]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>解决方式：编辑<code>/etc/apk/repositories</code>，删除链接前面存在的<code>#</code>。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
